code: @Override public void configure() {     from("aws-s3://bucket-name?amazonS3Client=#amazonS3Client&deleteAfterRead=false&maxMessagesPerPoll=25&delay=5000").log(LoggingLevel.INFO, "consuming", "Consumer Fired!").idempotentConsumer(header("CamelAwsS3ETag"), FileIdempotentRepository.fileIdempotentRepository(new File("target/file.data"), 250, 512000)).log(LoggingLevel.INFO, "Replay Message Sent to file:s3out ${in.header.CamelAwsS3Key}").to("file:target/s3out?fileName=${in.header.CamelAwsS3Key}"). }

@Produces @Named("amazonS3Client") AmazonS3 amazonS3Client() {     AWSCredentials credentials = new BasicAWSCredentials("XXXXX", "XXXXX").     AWSCredentialsProvider credentialsProvider = new AWSStaticCredentialsProvider(credentials).     AmazonS3ClientBuilder clientBuilder = AmazonS3ClientBuilder.standard().withRegion(Regions.US_WEST_1).withCredentials(credentialsProvider).     return clientBuilder.build(). }
